metadata.name: Xenobase - No.1
metadata.description:
In the distant future, AI has taken over.

'Many new inhabitants from all over the galaxy roam our lands and consume our skies. 
Looming behind almost every cloud in the southern hemisphere, You will catch a glimpse of a Xenomorph structure.' 

In this collection there art 4 unique captures of a Xenobase. 

Each artwork is AI generated in batches of 20, Where one will make the cut and 19 will be discarded.
Then the photoshopping starts. Colour adjustments, masking, boosting contrasts, adding, deleting, shading, etc. Until the finished piece is rendered.
